@CovidSolidarit1 @calirunnerdoc Yes, I am in Atlanta, Georgia, USA.
It has taken 13 months to be accepted into a treatment program after my stroke.  
Now that I have finally gotten tests &amp; scans showing damage, I have been moved to top of wait lists for care.  I've had to fight so hard to be seen &amp; heard.

@CovidSolidarit1 @calirunnerdoc I have more in depth MRI w contrast ordered &amp; lab work to find the cause of my strokes, find CSF leak  &amp; define clotting issues.  I'm happy to finally get validation &amp; answers to damages to my brain &amp; CNS but terrified what else it will mean. 
#TreatLongCovid 
#teamclots
